[2020-07-14 15:51] megasupp (mega-supp): > 2. It says that it is complicated to figure out an Engineer value in terms of its Energy + 1 Shield
@Deleted User  That is because in most cases you are either buying engi for energy to build more drones and won't need to sacrifice it on defence until like 4-6 turns into the future, which makes its BV=2*inflation^turns (which is hugely dependent on current boardstate) or you buy it for defence and just burn the energy so energy value is 0. Worth noting that because inflation changes with time, calculations which account for inflation of a big number of turns become less accurate.
